org.modelio.metamodel.uml.behavior.interactionModel

Interface InteractionFragment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<MObject>, Element, MObject, ModelElement, UmlModelElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CombinedFragment, ExecutionOccurenceSpecification, ExecutionSpecification, Gate, InteractionOperand, InteractionUse, MessageEnd, OccurrenceSpecification, PartDecomposition, StateInvariant, TerminateSpecification

    public interface InteractionFragment
extends UmlModelElement
    InteractionFragment v0.0.9054 InteractionFragment is an abstract notion of the most general interaction unit. An interaction fragment is a piece of an interaction. InteractionFragments sequencing information is handled by an internal feature that is not directly accessible. The Joni Java API provides methods to access the ordering of InteractionFragments.
